{"tid":485150,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"p牌超速15km以下使唔使加半年p","createTime":"2017-11-30T16:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T07:26:52.000Z","uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4e69848ff9f29a435348b285ba959f45935c5c1c","tid":485150,"uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T16:45:24.000Z","msg":"見有巴打開post問衝燈，好奇問下如果p牌超速15km以下使唔使加半年p<br />\n運輸署寫就話扣3或5分就加半年，10分就重考<br />\n咁超15km唔使扣分，係咪即是齋交錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a5b3a570c8f1569fadd4de0f416c74801b26cd","tid":485150,"uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T16:53:14.000Z","msg":"假設條路限70<br />\n但行緊75<br />\n都加半年？"},{"pid":"77d38733d2cf2ec139e0b1967757521433fc0e8e","tid":485150,"uid":13645,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:32:32.000Z","msg":"巴打閱讀理解拎F?"},{"pid":"6dfe509386fedac70d42e87544bcf3f87a5ed474","tid":485150,"uid":16050,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T19:33:12.000Z","msg":"留意個或字。「70km以上」本身係一條額外規矩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n// 倘持有暫准駕駛執照的司機觸犯一次「輕微」道路交通違例事項﹝即是根據《道路交通﹝違例駕駛記分﹞條例》﹝第 375 章﹞第 4 條，可令駕駛者<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">被記 3 分或 5  分違例事項</span>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">或</span></span>在這項暫准駕駛執照計劃中所引入的<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">四項限制中</span>任何一項﹞，一經定罪，其暫准駕駛期將 延長 6 個月。<br />\n<br />\n四項限制之一：<br />\n(c) 即使在車速限制超過每小時 70 公里的路段行駛，亦<span style=\"color: gold;\">不得以超過每小時 70 公里</span>的車速駕駛車輛 //"},{"pid":"52b74428b8693a0314361fdd4303fcd19ca5db9d","tid":485150,"uid":23416,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T19:51:58.000Z","msg":"都唔知邊個諗出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825889919f78968cd815d0b618a6af0e9ce5e56a","tid":485150,"uid":47023,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T23:43:21.000Z","msg":"試過p牌果陣70行84超左14， 罰錢了事"},{"pid":"aa1125639028a2c331fd299a6f1