ts/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （好似係）"},{"pid":"477c329a09f78f3b653534c3ba68b2b161f8389c","tid":485150,"uid":28928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T04:20:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實點知我係p牌 架車貼p唔等於揸果個係p 咁架車係行100既路到行90 邊個會影佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n部車貼左P牌，就算你唔係p牌果個，都要跟返P牌規則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （好似係）</blockquote><br />\n唔洗"},{"pid":"a75788a0cbef6537c5452ce1851196f297ef707e","tid":485150,"uid":120850,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T04:43:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實點知我係p牌 架車貼p唔等於揸果個係p 咁架車係行100既路到行90 邊個會影佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n部車貼左P牌，就算你唔係p牌果個，都要跟返P牌規則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （好似係）</blockquote><br />\n唔洗</blockquote><br />\n你係法官？定律政司"},{"pid":"532b71138f2e8711a49d366e40e25c4cbd278cb2","tid":485150,"uid":5020,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T04:58:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實點知我係p牌 架車貼p唔等於揸果個係p 咁架車係行100既路到行90 邊個會影佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n部車貼左P牌，就算你唔係p牌果個，都要跟返P牌規則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （好似係）</blockquote><br />\n唔洗</blockquote><br />\n你係法官？定律政司</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔使係法官同律政師<br />\n有眼識睇中英文就可以睇返法律上寫咩<br />\n<br />\n法律上只有寫拎住暫准駕駛執照<br />\n必須在車輛上展示P 字牌<br />\n<br />\n但法律上無明文寫過正式駕駛執照嘅人<br />\n喺車輛上展示P 字牌 有咩後果<br />\n<br />\n依我以前嘅經驗<br />\n交警見你掛P又行超過70<br />\n一定的你埋路邊<br />\n如果正式牌揸車，車上有P 牌<br />\n睇交警心情係屌你一句定兩句<br />\n法律上無任何罰則可以畀佢寫落簿<br />\n<br />\nps: google 下好難？<br />\n<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140410/00410_098.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140410%2F00410_098.html&d=q3wpS3Rju0vDUCG9chlp3W6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=c06c91f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140410/00410_098.html</a><br />\n執業大律師陸偉雄指現時一些正式駕駛執照持有者會在車上掛「P牌」，法例上沒違規，也無須遵守「P牌」守則，「但這樣會令執法者更難執法，其他道路使用者也無所適從。」"},{"pid":"e62f210c1dde49a98d5034a55b8356cf4d00c202","tid":485150,"uid":78574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T01:43:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實點知我係p牌 架車貼p唔等於揸果個係p 咁架車係行100既路到行90 邊個會影佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n部車貼左P牌，就算你唔係p牌果個，都要跟返P牌規則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （好似係）</blockquote><br />\n唔洗</blockquote><br />\n你係法官？定律政司</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔使係法官同律政師<br />\n有眼識睇中英文就可以睇返法律上寫咩<br />\n<br />\n法律上只有寫拎住暫准駕駛執照<br />\n必須在車輛上展示P 字牌<br />\n<br />\n但法律上無明文寫過正式駕駛執照嘅人<br />\n喺車輛上展示P 字牌 有咩後果<br />\n<br />\n依我以前嘅經驗<br />\n交警見你掛P又行超過70<br />\n一定的你埋路邊<br />\n如果正式牌揸車，車上有P 牌<br />\n睇交警心情係屌你一句定兩句<br />\n法律上無任何罰則可以畀佢寫落簿<br />\n<br />\nps: google 下好難？<br />\n<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140410/00410_098.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140410%2F00410_098.html&d=q3wpS3Rju0vDUCG9chlp3W6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=c06c91f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140410/00410_098.html</a><br />\n執業大律師陸偉雄指現時一些正式駕駛執照持有者會在車上掛「P牌」，法例上沒違規，也無須遵守「P牌」守則，「但這樣會令執法者更難執法，其他道路使用者也無所適從。」</blockquote><br />\n唔犯法但好撚無品囉<br />\n除左個牌好撚麻煩咩?"},{"pid":"6f184dc43731f77ba04c59d5cb1c9027dac52141","tid":485150,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T01:44:12.000Z","msg":"唔洗 純罰錢"}]}